long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Extract keywords with search volumes from Google Planner with a single click. They are automatically copied to your clipboard, ready for you to paste (CTRL+V) wherever you want.

Important note!
To copy all of the keywords, you must scroll to the very bottom of the list.

The simplest SEO tool, you've always wanted.
